{
  "texts": [
    "For the subsampled set of 20k instances, CPLEX was executed with the parameter \"threads\" set to 1, restricting CPLEX to single-threaded mode.",
    "This option is only available when using the \"CMD\"-version of CPLEX in pulp.",
    "For comparisons with RASCAL, the RDKit implementation in version 2023.09.3 was used; the time limit was set to one hour.",
    "As described above, for part of the comparison the similarity thresholds were modified.",
    "To obtain approximations when no exact computations were performed, the option \"returnEmptyMCES\" was enabled."
  ]
}